platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Freedom awaits prisoners who survive the treacherous journey through Mount Grimrockthough, as youre quietly informed, youd be the first. That promise-slash-dare primed us for exactly the kind of spectacle this first-person dungeon-crawler delivers. Before long, youre nabbing mighty weapons, battling ogres and other beasties, and guiding your party past diabolical traps. Gleefully old-school, Legend of Grimrock pays tribute to classics like Dungeon Master and Ultima Underworld with an enormously fun adventure.
